description:
"Peace, Be Still" - three words that had power over the wind and waves when spoken by Jesus, as the lake immediately turned to calm. These are also three words that can have power over the dark forces in our lives when we abide in Jesus. The disciples witnessed the creative power of Jesus before their eyes, and we can also experience that today.
